{"tid":1383301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 中前線既同我入黎 有野要大家達成共識","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:17:17.000Z","uid":137632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da5fb0e51d767f1322c7ca041cf6aa69f2c96ef5","tid":1383301,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"小弟之前都開左個post講關於香城online入面 再處於死守階段<br />\n<br />\n打算比壓力班黑警係冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地必須 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反守為攻</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但咁做既 我地需要兩樣野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一: 人手</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二: 戰力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依個post想睇下有幾多人會贊成 同 願意幫手係好機會既情況下一齊衝上前<br />\n(例如 西邊圍得幾十隻狗 我地有幾萬人咁)<br />\n<br />\n我今日睇左個post搵唔返 <br />\n希望有人post link <br />\n大概<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰術</span>就係<br />\n第一排拎<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盾</span><br />\n第二排<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遠攻</span><br />\n第三排<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">近戰</span><br />\n<br />\n正評 : 會上前 一齊衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評 : 民意反彈 需智取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce1f56dba0aadd1516b3918bff52331a1d32b3d","tid":1383301,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"到時繼續捱打 定搏一搏 為樽頸位作出犧牲 <br />\n大家請作出決定"},{"pid":"9bdea46e825b9ffa343b2a840c57cfd736c1ff3c","tid":1383301,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"大家要知道 革命 